{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; EXTRACTO DE DECRETO N&#xB0; 495 EXENTO, DE 1993 </div></div>", "i": 5944919}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Por Decreto Exento N&#xB0; 495 de fecha 23 de Septiembre de 1993 del Ministerio de Educaci&#xF3;n, se sustituy&#xF3; el inciso primero del art&#xED;culo &#xFA;nico del Decreto Exento de Educaci&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 33 de 1983 por el siguiente nuevo:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Autor&#xED;zase el funcionamiento del Instituto Profesional que se indica, organizado por la persona jur&#xED;dica que se se&#xF1;ala:</div><br><div class=\"p\"> Nombre de la Instituci&#xF3;n:&nbsp; Instituto&nbsp;  Profesional</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CAMPUS o Instituto Nacional</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; de Computaci&#xF3;n y</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Administraci&#xF3;n de Empresas</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INDAE.</div><div class=\"p\"> Domicilio&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; Santiago.</div><div class=\"p\"> Organizador&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  :&nbsp; Sociedad &quot;Instituto</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Nacional de Computaci&#xF3;n y</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Administraci&#xF3;n de Empresas</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; INDAE Limitada o CAMPUS</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &